      "content": "but that's just what people say to be polite. the truth is, they're stuck. they're stuck because of me. if i wasn't here, they could travel, they could focus on their own families, they wouldn't have to spend every weekend in a hospital waiting room. wouldn't it be better if they could just move on and live their lives without this constant weight?",
